# A static executable links and runs where the platform supports it (musl or MSVC); the scripted excludeFilter gates
# this fixture to those cells. checkStatic asserts the platform-appropriate result: a fully-static binary on musl (ldd
# reports nothing), or a static C runtime on MSVC (dumpbin shows no CRT DLL import). The fail-fast on unsupported
# platforms (glibc, macOS) is covered by LinkSuite.
> run
> checkStatic
